<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">

<html lang="es" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head>
<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Recuperación de Contraseña - Grupo Martí</title>
<style type="text/css">
        /* Client-specific Styles */
        #outlook a { padding: 0; }
        .ReadMsgBody { width: 100%; }
        .ExternalClass { width: 100%; }
        .ExternalClass, .ExternalClass p, .ExternalClass span, .ExternalClass font, .ExternalClass td, .ExternalClass div { line-height: 100%; }
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
        table { border-collapse: collapse !important; }
        body { height: 100% !important; margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; background-color: #faf8ff; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; }

        /* Mobile Styles */
        @@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { width: 100% !important; }
            .content-padding { padding: 20px !important; }
            .code-box { font-size: 32px !important; letter-spacing: 4px !important; }
        }
    </style>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/></head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #faf8ff;">
<center>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #faf8ff;" width="100%">
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0 40px 0;">
<!-- Email Container -->
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="container" style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);" width="600">
<!-- Header -->
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center" bgcolor="#135bec" style="padding: 40px 0 40px 0;">
<img alt="Grupo Martí Logo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCRjdJ0c22rlF_9W7aS2Dy-xVQRUxgaixSG2L_mcX0rqrrcmgfinReasd44mLHw6_5XGUK2e3uQN7o1IfgGWlhZ344Z5i-RiOOusvisI3rpaiBuo8qXrQ4G8FCwhxRCrAnkvWTMFLhk5EyebJcOgjqP4la_TBVdwHbaUCzpgCQqUYitPj3nwFCF2IPC5rtdEvTWvbv-QBImeBrnqbL4s1oC_iIVM10rKbpASlMPcH140aP8VV9B43E5D2dZQcyzB4rS4wIJceuJPBoG" style="display: block; border: 0;" width="180"/>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- Body Content -->
<tr>
<td class="content-padding" style="padding: 40px 40px 30px 40px;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tbody><tr>
<td style="color: #191b24; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 32px; padding-bottom: 24px;">
                                            Recuperación de Contraseña
                                        </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="color: #434655; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding-bottom: 20px;">
                                            Hola <strong>@Model.payload.nombre</strong>,
                                        </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="color: #434655; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding-bottom: 32px;">
                                            Hemos recibido una solicitud para restablecer la contraseña de tu cuenta en el <strong>Portal de Proveedores de Grupo Martí</strong>. Si no realizaste esta solicitud, puedes ignorar este correo de forma segura.
                                        </td>
</tr>
<!-- Code Box -->
<tr>
<td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 32px;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f3f3ff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed #135bec;" width="100%">
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center" style="padding: 24px;">
<div style="color: #135bec; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase;">
                                                            CÓDIGO DE RECUPERACIÓN
                                                        </div>
<div class="code-box" style="color: #0045bd; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 8px;">
                                                            @Model.payload.code
                                                        </div>
<div style="color: #737687; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px;">
                                                            Expira en 1 hora
                                                        </div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- Action Button -->
<tr>
<td align="center" style="padding-bottom: 32px;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: separate;">
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center" bgcolor="#135bec" style="border-radius: 4px;">
<a href="@Model.payload.url" style="padding: 14px 32px; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;" target="_blank">Restablecer Contraseña</a>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- Divider -->
<tr>
<td style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 24px;">
<p style="color: #737687; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; margin: 0;">
                                                Si el botón no funciona, copia y pega el siguiente enlace en tu navegador:
                                            </p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">
<a href="@Model.payload.url" style="color: #135bec; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: underline;">@Model.payload.url</a>
</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- Footer -->
<tr>
<td bgcolor="#f8fafc" style="padding: 30px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tbody><tr>
<td style="color: #585e6d; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; text-align: center;">
                                            ¿Necesitas ayuda técnica? Contacta a: <a href="mailto:soporte.proveedores@marti.mx" style="color: #135bec; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">soporte.proveedores@marti.mx</a>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-top: 20px; color: #737687; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">
                                            GRUPO MARTÍ © 2026
                                        </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-top: 12px; text-align: center;">
<a href="#" style="color: #737687; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; text-decoration: underline; margin: 0 8px;">Aviso de Privacidad</a>
<span style="color: #c3c5d8;">|</span>
<a href="#" style="color: #737687; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; text-decoration: underline; margin: 0 8px;">Términos y Condiciones</a>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</center>
</body></html>